      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>Cognitive function</strong>
        <p>Even mild iodine insufficiency in adults is associated with reduced cognitive performance, poor concentration, and increased fatigue — symptoms often attributed to other causes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

